Areva Gets Potential EU1.2B German Wind Contract, Echos Says

-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 
2011-11-28T05:14:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-28/areva-gets-potential-eu1-2b-german-wind-contract-echos-says.html
Areva SA has won a wind power
contract with a potential value of 1.2 billion euros ($1.6
billion) in  Germany , French daily  Les Echos  reported, citing
unidentified people.  The contract, for 120 wind turbines, is subject to Areva
being able to secure financing, Les Echos said. The figure of
1.2 billion euros would include servicing costs, the newspaper
added.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  